'''Junglee Toofan Tyre Puncture''' was a show broadcast on [[Zee TV]] during the early 90s. One of the first shows to be aired on Zee TV, the channel usually began its shows with this program. It was targeted towards the kids with puppet shows and interesting anecdotes.
It was based on [[Sesame street]].
